Getting There

Air Travel

Flying round trip to Maui

Due to the spike in competition over the last few years, flying to Maui has become much more accessible. All of the major airlines including: American, United, and Delta fly daily out of their major hubs. Other airlines flying directly to Maui also include Alaskan and Hawaiian Airlines. Recently, Southwest Airlines was approved by the FAA to start operating flights to Hawaii flying direct from San Jose and Oakland. One of the easiest ways to compare all flights is to use Google Flights.
